{"word":"ἀντίδοτος","slug":"ἀντίδοτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀντίδοτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀντιδίδωμι'><el>ἀντιδίδωμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>given in lieu of</i>, <el>πυρός</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>given as a remedy for</i>, <el>κακῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>:—as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>, <el>ἀντίδοτος, ἡ</el>, <i>an antidote</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}